{"tid":211071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被控掌摑途人　海關督察疑庭內自拍　多張相片上載FB","createTime":"2017-04-21T11:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T12:40:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14fe9b1bb06195b2fbdb14174eecc5af1565b040","tid":211071,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/21/192544_779ae98597ee866431080ce5dacb8575.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F21%2F192544_779ae98597ee866431080ce5dacb8575.jpg&h=95b2fe30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名海關督察因涉嫌掌摑及恐嚇途人被控，昨日在東區法院接受審訊。他昨日隨即在Facebook上載多張相片，懷疑是他昨日在庭內自拍及偷拍主控官。<br />\n<br />\n43歲海關督察方富邦被指去年9月15日在銅鑼灣觸犯襲擊及刑事恐嚇罪，案件昨開審並押後至下周三裁決。方富邦被指在聆訊時呼喝證人，又不時冷笑及搖動手腳，更大聲與官理論，被官斥責：「做乜咁大聲同我講嘢？你質問我？你邊位呀！」<br />\n<br />\n昨午1時許，方富邦在Facebook上載了四張相片，並寫上一句「扮案......」。相片相信是他在洗手間及庭內的自拍照，另一張疑似是庭上偷拍了主控官黎安妮大律師及旁邊警員的背影。至昨晚10時許方富邦再上載照片，懷疑是掌摑途人黃穎賢在庭外等候時被偷拍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%8E%8C%E6%91%91%E9%80%94%E4%BA%BA-%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E7%9D%A3%E5%AF%9F%E7%96%91%E5%BA%AD%E5%85%A7%E8%87%AA%E6%8B%8D-%E5%A4%9A%E5%BC%B5%E7%9B%B8%E7%89%87%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%89fb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%258E%258C%25E6%2591%2591%25E9%2580%2594%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%259D%25A3%25E5%25AF%259F%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%258B%258D-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%2589%2587%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25BC%2589fb%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n33Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=b6e782c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%258E%258C%25E6%2591%2591%25E9%2580%2594%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%259D%25A3%25E5%25AF%259F%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%258B%258D-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%2589%2587%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25BC%2589fb%2F&h=2c06a1fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%8E%8C%E6%91%91%E9%80%94%E4%BA%BA-%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E7%9D%A3%E5%AF%9F%E7%96%91%E5%BA%AD%E5%85%A7%E8%87%AA%E6%8B%8D-%E5%A4%9A%E5%BC%B5%E7%9B%B8%E7%89%87%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%89fb/</a>"},{"pid":"075e3ceda01aad43d1808590d43669c29e3294e8","tid":211071,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"真痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3da7294dcf1a32ac103209a0bb250137fd76ff","tid":211071,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:12:38.000Z","msg":"應該坐得監"},{"pid":"22c72580770a94e60523b054a5bf053e1a7ff735","tid":211071,"uid":104260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:20:23.000Z","msg":"Annie Lai 好靚女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32340924a19bb33c52fb015e973263e1c91515e","tid":211071,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:22:29.000Z","msg":"點解呢d痴線佬都入到海關做<br />\n<br />\n定係因為入海關先做到痴左線"},{"pid":"103be8ec87ece49ba765947261021c31285faeaf","tid":211071,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:26:44.000Z","msg":"以為自己係何君搖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"31a26fff9a3e9bbf2e5bcec5f07ffb4628b6b4ed","tid":211071,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:30:15.000Z","msg":"痴線佬都做得海關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68213f2c3fa7d58d9782c696d0c0144e1e6ba7f1","tid":211071,"uid":16364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re